Tags:
  - 873
By: Eckhart
Commentary: Knowledge alone delivers; method and contemplation make the
  psychic terrain propitious for this event.
---
Of what does this true possession of God consist, when one really has him? It
depends on the heart and an inner, intellectual return to God and not on
steady contemplation by a given method.
